Fonts are from the Terminus package (https://terminus-font.sourceforge.net/).

The CP437 fonts aren't distributed with Ubuntu so you need to download the 
source and build them (make -j8 psf). From version 4.49.1.

The pdf is built using tools from https://www.zap.org.au/projects/console-fonts-zap/
  * psf2psftx
  * psftx-codechart

Font converted (.psf -> .cpp)
  * gcc fontconv.c -o fontconv
  * fontconv font.psf > font.cpp



